Removed "Thug Life" as I have been unable to find any reliable sources to verify filming has begun. Reports from Nov. 6/7, when the film title was announced, say that filming is expected to begin "next month", which I take to mean December. But I haven't found any reports that it has actually started. Per [[WP:ACCESSIBILITY]] and [[MOS:TABLECAPTION]], data tables should always include a descriptive caption.
